ihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/d6KQzNf.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd6KQzNf.gif&h=b3ebd9eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>一名市民於金鐘橋底下，遭警員<span style=\"color: red;\">以布袋彈瞄準頭部射擊</span>。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同場加映：<br />\n示威者吐血<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/hRCPds07zSM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FhRCPds07zSM&d=BSpFugi7VYdA%2F48z81zRmUcGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=74975088\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/hRCPds07zSM</a> <br />\n<br />\n拖行暈倒示威者<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/GfhHJqNVPig\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FGfhHJqNVPig&d=BSpFugi7VYdA%2F48z81zRmUcGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=36056931\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/GfhHJqNVPig</a> <br />\n<br />\n唔比救護車入<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/mT8SH2EJctk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FmT8SH2EJctk&d=BSpFugi7VYdA%2F48z81zRmUcGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=70c461cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/mT8SH2EJctk</a> <br />\n<br />\n地鐵站噴椒<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/sQk9mLw07WM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FsQk9mLw07WM&d=BSpFugi7VYdA%2F48z81zRmUcGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=0b1b3b45\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/sQk9mLw07WM</a> <br />\n<br />\n開槍<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/9bbFANmVWZ4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F9bbFANmVWZ4&d=BSpFugi7VYdA%2F48z81zRmUcGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=1dce89a0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/9bbFANmVWZ4</a> <br />\n<br />\n向記者放tear gas<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/cWZ0R67V5Yg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FcWZ0R67V5Yg&d=BSpFugi7VYdA%2F48z81zRmUcGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=46a72fb6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/cWZ0R67V5Yg</a> <br />\n<br />\n<br />